flowchart TD
U[User Message] --> L[Language Detection]
L --> P1[Policy Guardrail]
P1 -->|Violation| R1[Policy Refusal Response]
P1 --> P2[Distress Detection]
P2 -->|Distress Detected| E1[Escalation Queue — CRITICAL]
P2 --> P3[Responsible Gaming Detector]
P3 -->|RG Signal| E2[RG Escalation — HIGH]
P3 --> P4[Fraud / Security Detector]
P4 -->|Security Risk| E3[Security Escalation — HIGH]
P4 --> P5[Circumvention Detector]
P5 -->|Welfare subtype| E4[Welfare Escalation — HIGH]
P5 -->|Fraud subtype| E5[Fraud Escalation — HIGH]
P5 --> S1[Account Service]
S1 -->|Match| A1[Account Response]
S1 --> S2[Payment Service]
S2 -->|Match| A2[Payment Response]
S2 --> S3[Promotions Service]
S3 -->|Match| A3[Promotions Response]
S3 --> K1[Game Rules Keyword Match]
K1 -->|Match| A4[Game Rules Response]
K1 --> K2[FAQ Keyword Match]
K2 -->|Match| A5[FAQ Response]
K2 --> C1[Cache Service]
C1 -->|Cache Hit| A6[Cached Response]
C1 --> V1[Semantic Retrieval FAISS]
V1 -->|Similarity Match| A7[Semantic Response]
V1 --> LLM[LLM Fallback]
LLM --> A8[Generated Response]
A1 --> O[Response Builder]
A2 --> O
A3 --> O
A4 --> O
A5 --> O
A6 --> O
A7 --> O
A8 --> O
O --> LOG[Audit Logger]
LOG --> UI[Streamlit UI]
